  "texts": [
    "Motivation of the Study: Federated learning is an emerging area of research that integrates advanced privacy-preserving techniques.",
    "However, this growing field has attracted attackers and created security vulnerabilities.",
    "Consequently, different security mechanisms have been developed to protect user privacy and detect malicious clients in the FL environment.",
    "These mechanisms encompass intrusion detection systems (IDS), which include authentication, access control, key management, and encryption.",
    "However, this review concentrates exclusively on IDS incorporating neural network models, feature engineering methods, and privacy-preserving techniques."
  ],
